IR Sensor Information:
The sensor thats currently in use is: https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B06XYNDRGF/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_asin_title_o07_s01?ie=UTF8&psc=1
The sensor has three leads, when looking at it with the black facing you, from left to right its pinout is (output pin, ground, vcc).
Those leads are to be hooked up to the pi on the pi's 5v output pin to sensors vcc pin, the pi's ground to the sensors ground, and the 
pi's GPIO #11 (can be changed in the code) to the sensors output pin.
